I read this book in 2005, but never posted this review. So here it is&hellip;
Growing a Business by Paul Hawken This is an honest and practical guide to running a business. I don&rsquo;t remember where I first heard about this book. Maybe Lars?
It was written in 1987. Hawken talks about building a business. It&rsquo;s often portrayed as a heroic or glamorous endeavor, but really it&rsquo;s not. It&rsquo;s a lot of hard work, but also a lot of common sense.
